.SH NAME
\fI\fBi.ortho.photo\fR\fR  \- Menu driver for the photo imagery programs.
.SH KEYWORDS
imagery, orthorectify, geometry
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBi.ortho.photo\fR
.br
